onal_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"The Games\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"the 33rd Olympiad\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few weeks\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"international glory\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's all you need to know about the latest edition of the quadrennial multi-sport showpiece.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the latest edition\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"the quadrennial multi-sport showpiece\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games will officially open on Friday, 26 July and will close on 11 August.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"26 July\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"11 August\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some sports, however, will get underway before the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some sports\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The football andrugby sevenstournaments will start on Wednesday, while the archery and handball competitions will begin on Thursday.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The football andrugby sevenstournaments\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the archery\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"handball competitions\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Various venues around France will be used for the Games, but most sports will be contested in Paris.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9989413738543405, \"rank\": 0.000871080763996701, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9082216164861314e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Various venues\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"most sports\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony will be held at the Jardins du Trocad\\u00e9ro (Gardens of the Trocadero) and the closing ceremony is at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"the Jardins du Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"(Gardens\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to ensure favourable conditions for the athletes, the surfing competition will be held in Tahiti.\", 